data.description: Beautifully Renovated Colonial Home Situated on over 24 acres with gorgeous meadow views but with the privacy of surrounding mature trees. This home boasts gleaming hardwood floors, added recessed lighting, soaring 2 story foyer, sleek & stylish kitchen with granite counter tops, bar seating, gas cooktop, double wall ovens, Grand Master Suite with vaulted ceiling, WIC, Private Master Bath with a double shower, double sinks & water closet, fully finished basement, 4 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms (there is a full batheroom on all 3 levels), wrap around Trex/Composite Deck, 2 car attached garage, 14 stall Barn with electric, water, work room & chicken nesting, green house, riding trails with a creek running around the property.  Some of the many recent updates completed include: Roof, Asphalt Driveway, Composite Deck, main level Hardwood Flooring, Leaf Filter, Green House, Garage Door, Master bath completely renovated, update basement bath, Blinds, Water Softener, laundry machine, oven, barn electricity, over $132,000 in upgrages.  Property has amazing potential for Horses, Livestock, Farming Produce, Hunting or a Retreat Getaway. Lovely Country Atmosphere with a short drive to commuter routes and shopping.
